CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 16, 1956, pg. 3, reads: "Mrs. Maria E. Carter, who died last week in Philadelphia, shown in her latest photo with her husband and son, Dr. William B. Carter (left) and W. Beverly Carter Jr., publisher of The Pittsburgh Courier - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dr. William B. Carter, Maria E. Carter, and Pittsburgh Courier publisher W. Beverly Carter seated in front of leaf patterned curtain
